message:
Multiple fixes

- remove unnecessary files in bin/data folder in order to save on final
binary. That includes, not including TuioRouter folder for an iOS
release for instance. We are currently copying asserts from project,
since still haven't found a good symlink solution;

- using astyle so that code looks nice when previewing in Github;

- refactored to #if defined everywhere;

- ofLog doesn't need `endl` at the end;

- changed ofLog calls so that don't change level at every one;

- different `drawModules()` according to platform;

- forward declaration of class Touch fix;

- detect if iPad or iPhone at runtime, since the variable we were using
of `TARGET_OF_IPHONE` is in version 0.9.3 being defined for both when in
iphone and ipad.

Fixes #13

